*** NEW QUEST: The Orc Fortress ***

A dark stronghold has been discovered beyond the fortress to the north!
Brave adventurers may now venture into the Orc Fortress -- a dangerous
12-room dungeon filled with orc warriors, a treacherous armory, dark
cells, and towering walls. At the heart of it all, the Orc Warlord
awaits on his throne. Do you have what it takes to defeat him?

To begin, travel to the fortress and look for a way north.

Good luck, adventurer. You'll need it.
